<BaseLayout title="Exotic Pets" description="Browse our comprehensive guide to exotic pets including reptiles, amphibians, birds, and small mammals.">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Exotic Pets Directory</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-pastel-pink rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Explore our comprehensive database of exotic pets. Each species page includes care requirements, 
        habitat needs, dietary information, legal considerations, and more.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
